-And who's that woman?

31:22.180 --> 31:24.090
-Always questions.

31:25.110 --> 31:27.090
-I like to know who I'm working with.

31:28.200 --> 31:31.100
-You mean "you're working for?"

31:31.110 --> 31:34.020
Don't get ahead of yourself, Alberto.

31:34.030 --> 31:35.100
-So who is she?

31:37.140 --> 31:39.050
-Ines: Sylvia Garcia.

31:39.060 --> 31:41.060
The biggest hash dealer on Costa Del Sol.

31:47.020 --> 31:49.090
-(engine rumbling) -(indistinct chatter)

31:54.100 --> 31:55.140
-Lotti: What is it?

31:57.110 --> 31:59.000
What do you see?

31:59.010 --> 32:00.220
-Charlie: There's our Catalan friends.

32:04.090 --> 32:06.010
-(instrumental music)

32:07.130 --> 32:10.050
-Lotti, that looks like the boat that hit us on the way to Spain.

32:14.070 --> 32:16.110
-Shit.

32:16.120 --> 32:18.090
I think you're right, Charlie.

32:19.120 --> 32:21.190
-And if it is...

32:21.200 --> 32:23.120
that means...

32:28.050 --> 32:31.000
-(inaudible)

32:36.210 --> 32:38.190
-So what do you think, Albert?

32:38.200 --> 32:40.170
What have you figured out?

32:45.040 --> 32:47.100
-Ortega stole the truck from Garcia

32:47.110 --> 32:49.010
just so he could   give it back to her.

32:49.020 --> 32:51.140
