32:51.150 --> 32:53.090
That's why he had us   frame Cortez,

32:53.100 --> 32:55.110
so he could have his own man   in charge of security.

32:55.120 --> 32:58.120
He's offering her a secure flight path in from Morocco

32:58.130 --> 33:00.050
to San Toledo.

33:02.190 --> 33:04.130
He's fucking smart.

33:04.140 --> 33:06.090
-(bell dings) -(cheers and applause)

33:06.100 --> 33:08.120
-(speaking Spanish)

33:10.120 --> 33:11.120
-(bell dings)

33:14.220 --> 33:15.230
-Come on, Billy!

33:23.110 --> 33:24.170
-(cheers and applause)

33:35.130 --> 33:37.200
-Come on, Billy Boy! Let's go, son. Let's go!

33:37.210 --> 33:39.090
-(bell dings)

33:39.100 --> 33:42.040
-(cheers and applause)

33:45.150 --> 33:46.150
-(speaking Spanish)

33:50.060 --> 33:51.060
-(dinging)

33:56.000 --> 33:58.090
-Well done, son, well done! That's it, Billy Boy!

34:00.060 --> 34:01.170
-(ringing)

34:04.050 --> 34:06.050
-(grunting)

34:08.060 --> 34:09.090
-Venga!

34:11.020 --> 34:13.020
-(cheers and applause)

34:15.050 --> 34:16.220
-(Spanish styled rock music)

34:36.210 --> 34:38.120
-(cheering) -(rock music)

34:40.160 --> 34:42.070
-(grunting)

34:52.010 --> 34:53.100
-Come on, Billy.

34:54.060 --> 34:55.200
-Well done, well done, well done!

35:00.230 --> 35:02.230
-(cheers and applause)

35:05.170 --> 35:08.040
-Referee:  Uno, dos...  -(bell dings)

35:09.080 --> 35:11.030
-Hate 'Em: Billy, Billy. Come here.

