Rueben Cerro has never been beaten.

35:21.160 --> 35:23.070
-First time for everything.

35:23.080 --> 35:24.160
-(bell dings) -Come on, Billy Boy.

35:24.170 --> 35:25.190
-Come on, Billy.

35:25.200 --> 35:27.190
-(cheers and applause)

35:31.070 --> 35:33.000
-(rock music)

35:42.180 --> 35:43.210
-(scoffs)

35:44.220 --> 35:46.180
-♪ Come on,   get off my back ♪

35:46.190 --> 35:48.060
♪ I've been under attack ♪

35:48.070 --> 35:49.200
♪ I need a place to relax ♪

35:49.210 --> 35:51.160
♪ Peace! Whoo! ♪

35:51.170 --> 35:53.090
♪ Come on,   give me a break ♪

35:53.100 --> 35:54.230
♪ 'Cause this is   all I can take ♪

35:55.000 --> 35:58.080
♪ How did love   turn to hate, now? ♪

35:58.090 --> 36:00.030
♪ Won't you   get out of my way ♪

36:00.040 --> 36:01.160
♪ This ain't no place   you can stay ♪

36:01.170 --> 36:04.210
♪ I got a lot on my plate,   you see? ♪

36:04.220 --> 36:06.200
♪ I'm at the back   of the line ♪

36:06.210 --> 36:08.230
♪ I'm done   wasting my time ♪

36:09.000 --> 36:11.090
-(grunting)

36:11.100 --> 36:13.060
-(bell dings)

36:13.070 --> 36:15.160
-It was quite a coincidence

36:15.170 --> 36:17.110
the thugs Blanco sent you to hit

36:17.120 --> 36:18.210
stuck around to rob a gas station.

36:22.090 --> 36:24.110
Like your friend up there in the ring,

36:24.120 --> 36:25.120
you've got balls,

36:25.130 --> 36:27.000
and that's important,

36:27.010 --> 36:28.200
but don't let them cost you your head.

36:28.210 --> 36:32.050
-(cheering and applause)

36:32.060 --> 36:33.150
-Hate 'Em: Use your feet. Use your feet.

36:33.160 --> 36:36.030
Pick him off. Jab him up, okay?

36:36.040 --> 36:38.160
-(laughing)

36:38.170 --> 36:40.120
-(Hate 'Em continues, muffled)

36:42.000 --> 36:44.020
-(heart racing) -(bell dings)

